Plot

Siddique (Indrajith) is an employee in a well known advertising company based in Bangalore. He is working in the creative section. When he reaches Kochi as part of a transfer from the head office in Bangalore, it is completely a novel experience for him. At Kochi, he gets the help of his friend Veena (Remya Nambisan) who is a dancer. There Siddique acquaints Ichcha (Nivin Pauly) and decides to share accommodation with him. Ichcha's influence creates changes in the life of Siddique. Ichcha's ways and behavior seems strange and unusual to all and nobody can guess his peculiar personality. The following intriguing events in the life of Siddique and Ichcha plot the story of 'Arikil Oral'.
